{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回\"雨中人\"讲述了芮玮在暴雨中被黑堡双魔追杀，身受重伤濒临死亡之际，被一位与他长相酷似的玄衫公子所救。玄衫公子不仅用灵丹解除了芮玮身中的骨剑之毒，还恢复了他的功力，但条件是芮玮必须化装成他的替身，前往金陵简家住上一年半载。芮玮为了报恩，接受了这个条件，并在玄衫公子的指导下学会了\"惊涛拍岸\"、\"滔天巨浪\"、\"骇浪排空\"三招掌法。随后，芮玮换上玄衫公子的服饰，乘坐简家马车前往金陵简府。在途中，他成功瞒过了简家老仆\"血手黑煞\"章真命的试探，进入简府后又巧妙应对了丫环们的询问，最终抵达书房。本章通过芮玮的遭遇，展现了江湖的险恶与人性的复杂，同时也为后续故事的发展埋下了伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mo",
      "speaker_name": "人魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓芮的！今天让你逃掉，'人魔'柯轻农是你养的……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_mo",
      "speaker_name": "地魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "乖乖跟我们去见堡主，再逃被我'地魔'那印远抓着，叫你遍尝地狱十八刑的滋味……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mo",
      "speaker_name": "人魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二哥，别真真给你那小子逃掉了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_mo",
      "speaker_name": "地魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子中了我一剑，逃到这里已是奇迹，一定躲在哪棵树后，等下个闪电亮，谅他再也逃不掉！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mo",
      "speaker_name": "人魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倘若那小子不在附近，傻等在这里，那真是一头大呆鸟了啦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_mo",
      "speaker_name": "地魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真叫那小子逃掉，回去怎好向堡主交待？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mo",
      "speaker_name": "人魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在那里！在那里！躺在那里！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_mo",
      "speaker_name": "地魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子！看你还能逃不？先砍下你这双能逃的脚！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mo",
      "speaker_name": "人魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二哥！二哥！你怎么啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不快滚！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_mo",
      "speaker_name": "地魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三弟我们走，今天认栽啦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "救一个死人干吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫他装成自己，谁也发觉不了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下芮玮，承蒙阁下恩救，敢问高姓大名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跟我来！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恩公有何吩咐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快快服下！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下予芮玮恩同再造，不但解除在下身中骨剑之巨毒，尚且恢复功力，此恩芮某有生难忘！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！刚才追你的两人是黑堡双魔吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是'地魔'那印远、'人魔'柯轻农。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不用太感激我，我用世上两颗灵丹救你，倒有一个条件，待这个条件你做成了，你我恩惠不必再记心上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恩公有何吩咐，但请指示！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要你化装成我的替身。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不叫你做什么为难的事，只要你到我家去，住上一年半载。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这册内记载我家中的一切，你仔细背着．当不会出什么差错，现在你且跟我模拟一下动作。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你的功夫差得很。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恩公武艺高绝，在下正怕这是最大的破绽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我且传你三招，你将这三招练熟，我家的人便不会怀疑你是伪装的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第一招'惊涛拍岸'！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第二招'滔天巨浪'！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "注意啦！第三招'骇浪排空'！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "功力别谈，你能将三招架式练成，便成了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请恩公再演一遍。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他只要学一招，也就马虎算了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恩公赐教！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尚请恩公指正！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没什么错，我还有急事待办，现在把衣服换过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_shan_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一切小心为要，到了危急之时，我自会出面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_shou_hei_sha",
      "speaker_name": "血手黑煞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子回来啦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_shou_hei_sha",
      "speaker_name": "血手黑煞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最近公子身体可好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噜苏什么，赶快驾车。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仅就一辆马车便可看出，简家不知是多么豪富了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他有半年未回，想是这马车每天都到得胜门外等候一趟，直等了半年，才等到今天一趟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_shou_hei_sha",
      "speaker_name": "血手黑煞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子要从哪个门进去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从侧门进。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_shou_hei_sha",
      "speaker_name": "血手黑煞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子请！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_huan",
      "speaker_name": "丫环",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大公子回来了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我回来了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_huan",
      "speaker_name": "丫环",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大公子笑起来真俊呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你两人陪我到书房去吧！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_huan",
      "speaker_name": "丫环",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子怎么啦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_huan",
      "speaker_name": "丫环",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子回来啦！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_huan",
      "speaker_name": "丫环",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有你们的事了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_huan",
      "speaker_name": "丫环",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子可要先去拜见主母？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先回书房。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lai_ren",
      "speaker_name": "来人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "主母要见大公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    }
  ],
